snippet.title: Oirbo Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore a vast, hand-drawn Metroidvania spaceship as Oirbo! Uncover secrets, battle enemies, and navigate a labyrinth of mystery in this 2D action Metroidvania.

Get it on:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1074280/Oirbo?utm_source=yttrailer
GOG: https://www.gog.com/en/game/oirbo
Epic Store: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/oirbo-c063b7
